<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.0.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.w3schools.com/w3css/4/w3.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Raleway">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <title>ATN Shop</title>
<style>
    body{
        background-color: darkkhaki;
    }
</style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" style="height:700px;"
                        src="https://www.lego.com/cdn/cs/set/assets/blt009499ba796e9496/10257_alt5.jpg" alt="First slide">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" style="height:700px;" 
                     src="https://target.scene7.com/is/image/Target/GUEST_7d73166d-06d6-4832-9a4e-4e8df26ed71d?wid=488&hei=488&fmt=pjpeg" alt="Second slide">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" style="height:700px;"
                        src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcT0YkYQshR0p2DE7RgS4ruCLLEE_AeJZUr3xw&usqp=CAU"
                        alt="Third slide">
                </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
        </div>

        <h1 style="color:black; text-align: center;padding-top: 5px">This is my company product</h1>

        <div class="container text-center">
            <div class="card-group">
                <div class="row">
                    {{#each hasbro}}
                    <div class="card col-md-2 m-3">
                        <a href="/hasbro/detail/{{_id}}">
                            <img class="card-img-top mt-4" src="{{image}}" width="200" height="200">
                        </a>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h4 class="card-title text-success">{{name}}</h4>
                            <p class="card-text text-danger">${{price}}</p>

                        </div>
                        <a href="/hashbro/add"><button class="button"><span>Add to cart </span></button></a>

                    </div>
                    {{/each}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pagination -->
        <div class="w3-center w3-padding-32">
            <div class="w3-bar">
                <a href="#" class="w3-bar-item w3-button w3-hover-black">«</a>
                <a href="#" class="w3-bar-item w3-black w3-button">1</a>
                <a href="#" class="w3-bar-item w3-button w3-hover-black">2</a>
                <a href="#" class="w3-bar-item w3-button w3-hover-black">3</a>
                <a href="#" class="w3-bar-item w3-button w3-hover-black">4</a>
                <a href="#" class="w3-bar-item w3-button w3-hover-black">»</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Images of Me -->
        <div class="w3-row-padding w3-padding-16" id="about">
            <div class="w3-col m6">
                <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRvH1ch0xs-ZJ4NAkvZBz5P2ulG69e_gE8dpQ&usqp=CAU"
                    alt="Lego" style="width:100%">
            </div>
            <div class="w3-col m6">
                <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQzmRiXk4_-BvaYkAG0lW2mndTc8yIestsZFw&usqp=CAU7"
                    alt="Lego" style="width:100%">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w3-container w3-padding-large" style="margin-bottom:32px">
            <h4 style="text-align: center;"><b>About ATN Shop</b></h4>
            <p>Lego is a line of assembled toys belonging to the Lego Group based in Billund, Denmark. The name "Lego"
                stands for the first two letters of the two words leg godt, which means "play well".

                The company's flagship product, Lego, consists of colorful bricks that come together with a series of
                matching circular teeth, minifigures called minifigures, and many other parts. . Lego pieces can be
                assembled and connected in many different ways to build many objects such as: vehicles, tall buildings
                and people - can work,... Anything. Anything can be disassembled once assembled, and the pieces can be
                used to create other objects.

                The ATN Corporation started producing playable bricks in 1949. Since then, the global Lego subculture
                has grown. Development support for the Legoland movies, games, competitions and six theme parks is done
                under the company name. As of July 2015, 600 billion Lego parts have been produced.
                Come to our lego company, believe that everyone can satisfy their love not only lego but also objects.
            </p>
            <hr>
            <h2 style="text-align: center;">
                <em>"Wellcome to ATN Shop. Hope your experience to the best!"</em>
            </h2>


        </div>


        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.12.9/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv3Rn7W3mgPxhU9K/ScQsAP7hUibX39j7fakFPskvXusvfa0b4Q"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.0.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>